[2026-03-10T15:55:37Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TrzVEVEDqqgKbqXPVNRU2X","type":"tool_result","content":"{\"id\":\"cloche-1uz\",\"title\":\"Establish host.cloche vs container .cloche convention\",\"description\":\"Formalize the convention: host.cloche contains workflows that run on the host machine (e.g. the main workflow that orchestrates container runs, merges results). All other .cloche files define workflows that run inside containers. Update the DSL docs, workflow loading code, and daemon to enforce this split cleanly.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-09T10:10:40.49233334-07:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-09T10:38:21.033728769-07:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-09T10:38:21.033728769-07:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"title\":\"Implement orchestration loop in cloched\",\"description\":\"Event-driven orchestration loop inside cloched. Triggers on: daemon startup, run completion, and new cloche orchestrate CLI command. On trigger: for each project with orchestration enabled, query task tracker, check per-project concurrency limits, claim highest-priority task, generate prompt, dispatch run. Per-project config in .cloche/config.toml. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §1.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"Orchestrator triggers on startup, run completion, and manual command. Respects per-project concurrency limits. Dispatches runs for ready tasks.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:45.361039309-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.892779417-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T12:52:21.892779417-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-31r\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.705184919-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-43y\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.745875428-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-4cl\",\"title\":\"Remove Orchestrator subsystem\",\"description\":\"Delete the internal/orchestrator package and all its complexity: Orchestrator struct, HostRunner, RunWaiter, ProjectConfig, OnRunComplete callbacks, in-flight tracking, concurrency limits, task claiming, and the orchestrate RPC. Replace with the simple model: daemon runs the main workflow from host.cloche using the shared workflow engine. The main workflow manages its own looping and task selection.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-09T10:10:43.379251455-07:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-09T12:53:23.430330104-07:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-09T12:53:23.430330104-07:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-4cl\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-5dd\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-09T10:11:19.636855236-07:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-7q8\",\"title\":\"Add 'cloche orchestrate' command to start fresh orchestrator run\",\"description\":\"cloche orchestrate should start a fresh run of the orchestrator for the project, so we don't have to restart the daemon every time we want orchestration to begin.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-09T18:21:37.954754244-07:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-09T18:51:24.063800587-07:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-09T18:51:24.063800587-07:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-dzz\",\"title\":\"Add host.cloche and workflow step type for orchestrator\",\"description\":\"Add a host.cloche DSL file that defines an 'orchestrate' workflow running on the host machine. Add a new 'workflow' step type that dispatches a named container workflow run and waits for completion. Refactor the Go orchestrator to execute the host workflow instead of hard-coded logic. See docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:25:19.791216871-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.302965767-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.302965767-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-dzz\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-mk9\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:47.898728041-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"},{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-dzz\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-zar\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.027992794-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-g5c\",\"title\":\"Remove old 'cloche orchestrate' command\",\"description\":\"Remove the cloche orchestrate CLI command and its gRPC RPC. cloche loop covers the same intent better. Clean up references in usage text, server handler, and proto.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-10T07:20:28.105480149-07:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-10T08:49:46.904627933-07:00\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-jj7\",\"title\":\"Chore: add host.cloche and scripts/ to cloche project\",\"description\":\"After cloche-dzz merges and is installed, create .cloche/host.cloche and .cloche/scripts/prepare-prompt.sh in the cloche project, matching the default templates from cloche init. Restart cloched so it picks up the new orchestration workflow. Verify that the next orchestration cycle uses the host workflow path.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"- .cloche/host.cloche exists with the default orchestrate workflow\\n- .cloche/scripts/prepare-prompt.sh exists and is executable (0755)\\n- Both files are committed\\n- cloched restarted; next orchestration cycle logs show host workflow execution\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:26.803760641-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.433838658-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-06T14:24:45.433838658-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-jj7\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-dzz\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T11:42:48.174588443-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-jkb\",\"title\":\"Add cloche orchestrate CLI command\",\"description\":\"New CLI subcommand: cloche orchestrate. Sends a manual trigger to cloched to check all projects for ready work and dispatch runs. See docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md §1.\",\"acceptance_criteria\":\"cloche orchestrate triggers the orchestration loop. Returns feedback on what was dispatched.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:42:47.655694437-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-03T15:40:57.538361224-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-03T15:40:57.538361224-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-jkb\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-2ju\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T10:45:38.787031976-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-m6l\",\"title\":\"Wire web UI Trigger Orchestrator button to actual orchestrator\",\"description\":\"The web dashboard's Trigger Orchestrator button (POST /api/projects/{name}/trigger) is a stub that returns 202 without calling the orchestrator. Wire it up:\\n\\n1. Add an orchestrateFn field (func(ctx context.Context, projectDir string) (int, error)) to the web Handler struct.\\n2. Add a WithOrchestrateFunc HandlerOption to set it.\\n3. In handleAPITriggerOrchestrator, resolve the project name to its directory (via the run store's ListProjects), call orchestrateFn, and return the dispatched count or an error.\\n4. In cmd/cloched/main.go, pass web.WithOrchestrateFunc(...) when constructing the web handler, using the same function wired to the gRPC server's SetOrchestrateFunc.\\n5. Add a unit test in handler_test.go verifying the trigger endpoint calls the function and returns the count.\\n6. If orchestrateFn is nil, return 501 Not Implemented.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"estimated_minutes\":15,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-03T19:07:34.595694255-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-04T17:03:00.48870097-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-04T17:03:00.48870097-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"labels\":[\"orchestrator\",\"web\"]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-r3b\",\"title\":\"Investigate cloche orchestrate 'No ready work found' despite open tasks\",\"description\":\"cloche orchestrate returns 'No ready work found' even though bd list shows 4 open, unblocked P2 tasks. The daemon-side orchestrator state may not be syncing with the beads tracker, or the concurrency setting (overridden to 1) may be causing unexpected behavior. Investigate the daemon-side orchestration registration, gRPC handler flow, and in-memory inFlight tracking.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-07T08:55:13.252440805-08:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:59:57.818896386-08:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-07T18:59:57.818896386-08:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\"}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-r96\",\"title\":\"Rename host.cloche orchestrate workflow to main\",\"description\":\"The host.cloche 'orchestrate' workflow should be renamed to 'main'. This is the entry point workflow that cloched executes on startup for active projects. The name 'main' better communicates its role as the top-level workflow.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-09T10:10:34.158362284-07:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-09T10:46:07.060699612-07:00\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-09T10:46:07.060699612-07:00\",\"close_reason\":\"Closed\",\"dependencies\":[{\"issue_id\":\"cloche-r96\",\"depends_on_id\":\"cloche-1uz\",\"type\":\"blocks\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-09T10:11:19.544251588-07:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\"}]}","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01EmNnibDiBApwUA2G3spKT8","session_id":"d065b4bd-561d-4d97-a269-c4a0bb94c829","uuid":"50162001-eb13-4092-84ee-ec95212fda6f"}
